message:
Hey ya'll
The National Day of Prayer is happening THIS WEEK - May 4th

It is a little different this year being outside of the US Bank Stadium, but the focus is less about the musicians, speakers and the venue

It's about Jesus being the main event and for us to come together as one large body of believers to ask God for healing, revival, the small things and the big 

If anyone wants to go with me I will be riding the train over there for the night! Take a break from studying to worship the God who has blessed us with education here at the U of M
He is worthy of our praise.
